- ability to select entire backends (eg, load from io_jit/ rather than io/)
    - luajit bitop backend
    - lua-5.2 bitop backend
- ability for backends to call other backends (jit falls back to plain for u3)
- autodetect availability of struct, lstruct, or bit on load; choose backend accordingly
- error handling test suite
- backreferences, eg, "n:u4 $n*f8" rather than "n:u4", n.."*f8"
- format combinators
